      passage: `While conducting an interview for her book <i>Latina Authors and Their Muses</i>, editor Mayra Calvani asked Sarah Cortez, author of the memoir <i>Walking Home</i>, what ______ Cortez’s response was <i>Bury Me Deep</i> by Megan Abbott.`,
